Premises:
Inductive fmap : Set := V : fmap | I : fmap -> dart -> tag -> point -> fmap | L : fmap -> dim -> dart -> dart -> fmap
inv_hmap = fix inv_hmap (m : fmap) : Prop := match m with | V => True | I m0 x _ _ => inv_hmap m0 /\ prec_I m0 x | L m0 k0 x y => inv_hmap m0 /\ prec_L m0 k0 x y end : fmap -> Prop
predf = fun (m : fmap) (z : dart) => succ m one z /\ succ m zero (A m one z) : fmap -> dart -> Prop
F_1 = fun (m : fmap) (z : dart) => A m zero (A m one z) : fmap -> dart -> dart
inj_dart = fun (Df : dart -> Prop) (f : dart -> dart) => forall x x' : dart, Df x -> Df x' -> f x = f x' -> x = x' : (dart -> Prop) -> (dart -> dart) -> Prop Argument scopes are [function_scope function_scope]
inj_F_succf : forall m : fmap, inv_hmap m -> inj_dart (succf m) (F m)
F_F_1 : forall (m : fmap) (z : dart), inv_hmap m -> exd m z -> exd m (F_1 m z) -> F m (F_1 m z) = z
inj_cA_1 : forall (m : fmap) (k : dim), inv_hmap m -> inj_dart (exd m) (cA_1 m k)
inj_cA : forall (m : fmap) (k : dim), inv_hmap m -> inj_dart (exd m) (cA m k)
nd_card : forall m : fmap, ndN m = card (fmap_to_set m)
predf_exd_F_1 : forall (m : fmap) (z : dart), inv_hmap m -> predf m z -> exd m (F_1 m z)
not_exd_nil : forall m : fmap, inv_hmap m -> ~ exd m nil
F_1_nil : forall m : fmap, inv_hmap m -> F_1 m nil = nil
inj_A : forall (m : fmap) (k : dim), inv_hmap m -> inj_dart (succ m k) (A m k)
inj_A_1 : forall (m : fmap) (k : dim), inv_hmap m -> inj_dart (pred m k) (A_1 m k)
MA1.incls_rem : forall (m : fmap) (x : dart), inv_hmap m -> exd m x -> incls (MA1.Iter_rem m x) (fmap_to_set m)
surj_cA : forall (m : fmap) (k : dim), inv_hmap m -> surj_dart (exd m) (cA m k)
surj_cA_1 : forall (m : fmap) (k : dim), inv_hmap m -> surj_dart (exd m) (cA_1 m k)
MA1.Iter_f_f_1_i : forall (m : fmap) (i : nat) (z : dart), inv_hmap m -> exd m z -> Iter (MA1.f_1 m) i (Iter (MA1.f m) i z) = z
MA1.degree_uniform : forall (m : fmap) (z : dart) (i : nat), inv_hmap m -> exd m z -> MA1.degree m z = MA1.degree m (Iter (MA1.f m) i z)
MA1.period_uniform : forall (m : fmap) (z : dart) (i : nat), inv_hmap m -> exd m z -> MA1.Iter_upb m z = MA1.Iter_upb m (Iter (MA1.f m) i z)
MA0.Iter_plus_inv : forall (m : fmap) (z : dart) (p i : nat), inv_hmap m -> exd m z -> Iter (MA0.f m) p z = z -> Iter (MA0.f m) (p + i) z = Iter (MA0.f m) i z
MA1.Iter_plus_inv : forall (m : fmap) (z : dart) (p i : nat), inv_hmap m -> exd m z -> Iter (MA1.f m) p z = z -> Iter (MA1.f m) (p + i) z = Iter (MA1.f m) i z
MA1.Iter_f_f_1 : forall (m : fmap) (i j : nat) (z : dart), inv_hmap m -> exd m z -> (j <= i)%nat -> Iter (MA1.f_1 m) j (Iter (MA1.f m) i z) = Iter (MA1.f m) (i - j) z
inj_neq : forall n m : nat, neq n m -> Zne (Z.of_nat n) (Z.of_nat m)
MA1.exd_Iter_f_1 : forall (m : fmap) (n : nat) (z : dart), inv_hmap m -> exd m z < -> exd m (Iter (MA1.f_1 m) n z)
MA0.exd_Iter_f_1 : forall (m : fmap) (n : nat) (z : dart), inv_hmap m -> exd m z < -> exd m (Iter (MA0.f_1 m) n z)
MA1.exd_Iter_f : forall (m : fmap) (n : nat) (z : dart), inv_hmap m -> exd m z < -> exd m (Iter (MA1.f m) n z)
MA0.exd_Iter_f : forall (m : fmap) (n : nat) (z : dart), inv_hmap m -> exd m z < -> exd m (Iter (MA0.f m) n z)
MA1.Iter_mult : forall (m : fmap) (z : dart) (n p : nat), inv_hmap m -> exd m z -> Iter (MA1.f m) p z = z -> Iter (MA1.f m) (n * p) z = z
Zne_left : forall n m : Z, Zne n m -> Zne (n + - m) 0

fmap_ind : forall P : fmap -> Prop, P V -> (forall f0 : fmap, P f0 -> forall (d : dart) (t : tag) (p : point), P (I f0 d t p)) -> (forall f1 : fmap, P f1 -> forall (d : dim) (d0 d1 : dart), P (L f1 d d0 d1)) -> forall f2 : fmap, P f2
MA1.LP7 : forall (m : fmap) (z : dart) (s : set), inv_hmap m -> (card s <= ndN m)%nat -> let n0 := (ndN m - card s)%nat in let nr := MA1.Iter_upb_aux m z s in exds s (Iter (MA1.f m) n0 z) -> forall j : nat, (n0 < j <= nr - 1)%nat -> Iter (MA1.f m) n0 z <> Iter (MA1.f m) j z
